### Phase 4 — Phone Filter on Google Sheets (completed)
- Added filter to Google Sheets node: Column = `phone`, Value = expression
- Key lessons learned:
  - Expression must use `.toString()` to match text in sheet
  - Retell sends `from_number` as `+17037312723` (with +1 and plus sign)
  - Google Sheets stores phone as `17037312723` (no plus sign — sheets treats + as formula)
  - Fix: strip the plus sign in the expression: `{{ $json.body.call_inbound.from_number.replace('+', '') }}`
  - Real call payload path: `$json.body.call_inbound.from_number`
  - Always check Webhook node output in a real call execution to see exact payload Retell sends
- Tested with real phone call — agent correctly says airline and confirmation from sheet row

**Final filter expression:**
`{{ $json.body.call_inbound.from_number.replace('+', '') }}`

